Function: render_url

Description: Renders the given URL and intelligently prepends the baseurl when necessary.

Usage: {% include dynamo function="render_url" url="/media/2018/10/helloworld.png" -%}

Parameters:
    * url       (string) - The URL to be rendered.  If the URL is an absolute URL
                           containing the http or https protocol, the URL will be rendered
                           directly.  If the URL is a relatively URL, the function
                           prepends the site baseurl.
